race.comment: SO REBELLIOUS (2) resumes and rates well for this contest. Raced well in Open 2's in his brief initial preparation and has trialled twice at Warwick Farm in preparation. Draws a bit awkwardly but a bold run is likely. Wary of ELYSIUM (8), who debuts for a top Sydney stable. She's well-bred and has had five trials stretching back to May. Has an inside gate and the blinkers are on and which signals intent. BABYFACED ASSASSIN (1) has a key jockey switch to Collett today and has more to offer second-up. No surpise if he's in the finish. GLENN'S LEGACY (3) will be fitter and can fill a minor slot for the strong local yard.
